// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0003 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 515dfe06-cf2a-56e3-b8c8-588881ef0ddd

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
